headline: CDNS Boosts Physical AI With Spec-to-Packaged Chiplet Ecosystem
summary: Cadence unveils a spec-driven chiplet ecosystem with Arm and Samsung Foundry, aiming to cut integration risk and speed AI, data center and HPC designs.

headline: Cadence Announces Fourth Quarter and Fiscal Year 2025 Financial Results Webcast
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., January 07, 2026--Cadence (Nasdaq: CDNS) will hold its fourth quarter and fiscal year 2025 financial results webcast on Tuesday, February 17, 2026.
